dct_title_s: Brabantiae Belgarum Provinciae recens exactaque descriptio
dct_alternative_sm: Brabantiae Belgarvm Provinciae recens exactaqve descripti
dct_description_sm: Map of Brabant, the northern part of which is now the southern Netherlands and the southern part of which is northern Belgium, showing towns, roads, rivers and canals.
Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margins of map.
Shows topography, vegetation, waterways, ports, routes.
